-- BAA Said to Hire Banks for Bond Investor Meetings
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2012-01-12T12:25:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/baa-said-to-hire-banks-for-bond-investor-meetings.html
BAA Funding Ltd. hired BNP Paribas
SA and  HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA)  to organize bond investor meetings,
according to a banker with knowledge of the arrangements. The
company may sell Class A bonds in euros once the presentations
have been completed, the banker said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Martin at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net  